@startuml
title <font size=12>Sequence Diagram: Transaksi (Sampai Invoice Tampil)</font>

actor User
participant "Transaksi Form" as Form
participant "TransaksiController" as Controller
participant "Database" as DB
participant "Invoice View" as Invoice

User -> Form: Buka Form Transaksi
Form -> Controller: GET /transaksi (Load barang stok > 0)
Controller -> DB: Query Barang
DB --> Controller: Return Barang List
Controller --> Form: Display Form

User -> Form: Tambah items ke keranjang
User -> Form: Submit Transaksi (POST)
Form -> Controller: POST /transaksi (dengan cart data)

Controller -> DB: Start Transaction
Controller -> DB: Create Transaksi record
DB --> Controller: Return ID Transaksi

Controller -> DB: Cek stok untuk setiap item
alt Stok Cukup
  Controller -> DB: Create DetailTransaksi
  Controller -> DB: Decrement Stok Barang
  Controller -> DB: Hitung Total Harga
else Stok Tidak Cukup
  Controller --> User: Error: Stok tidak mencukupi
end

Controller -> DB: Update total_harga Transaksi
Controller -> DB: Log Activity (RecordAktivitas)
DB --> Controller: Commit Transaction

Controller -> Invoice: Redirect ke Invoice Page
Controller -> DB: Query Transaksi + DetailTransaksi + Barang
DB --> Invoice: Return Transaksi Data
Invoice --> User: Display Invoice

@enduml
